.TH "sfwbar-idleinhibit" "1" "" ""
.SH Name
sfwbar-idleinhibit \- Sfwbar IdleInhibitor module
.sp
Filename: idleinhibit.so
.sp
Requires: none
.SH SYNOPSIS
.sp
The IdleInhibit module, allows attaching idle inhibitor to any widget in the
taskbar. If an idle inhibitor is active on a visible widget, it will prevent
the compositor to going into an idle state (i.e. blanking a screen,
going into a suspend mode or activating a screensaver)
.SH Triggers
.sp
The module defines trigger \fIIdleInhibitor\fP which is emitted whenever the
state of any idle inhibitor changes.
.SH Functions
.SS IdleInhibitState([id:string])
.sp
Query an idle inhibitor state of a widget specified by \fIid\fP\&. If omitted, the
state of a widget calling the function will be returned. Returns a string
containing a value \fIOn\fP or \fIOff\fP\&.
.SS SetIdleInhibitor([id:string,] state:string)
.sp
Set idle inhibitor state for a widget. If parameter \fIid\fP is specified, the
function will set inhibitor state for a specified widget, otherwise it will be
set for the current widget.  The possible \fIstate\fP values are:
.INDENT 0.0
.TP
.B \(dqOn\(dq
turn on an idle inhibitor
.TP
.B \(dqOff\(dq
turn off an idle inhibitor
.TP
.B \(dqToggle\(dq
toggle the state of an idle inhibitor
.UNINDENT
